              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>37</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Joint authorisation process to grant individual rights of use for radio spectrum</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>UK legislation does not preclude joint authorisations. Ofcom’s current powers under the Wireless Telegraphy Act 2006 are sufficient to allow for a joint authorisation process</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
