              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p />
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Not required - most obligations fall on the European Commission and are not obligations for the UK. Those that are, are implemented by section 4A(2) and (3) of the Communications 2003</p>
