            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Article 40</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Security of network and services</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Article 40 is largely implemented by sections 105A to 105D of the Communications Act 2003.  The UK shortly intends to introduce a Telecommunications (Security) Bill that will strengthen the regulation of the security of networks and services</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Article 41</p>
