            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>45(1)</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p />
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Sections 3(3), 4(9) and (10) and 22 of the Communications Act 2003 and sections 2(3) 3(2)(d) and Schedule 1(3) of the Wireless Telegraphy Act 2006</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>45(2)</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p />
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Some provisions require no transposition as the obligation falls on the European Commission and Radio Spectrum Policy Group: other obligations implemented by sections 3(2)(a), 3(3), 3(4)(d) (e), 4(4) of the Communications Act 2003 and sections 3(2),8(3B), 9(7), 9ZA, 30 and Schedule 1 of the Wireless Telegraphy Act 200.</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>45(3)</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p />
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>General duties of Ofcom in sections 3 and 7 of the Communications Act 2003 and section 3 of the Wireless Telegraphy Act 2006</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>45(4)</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p />
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Sections 4(6),4(6A) and 5 of the Communications Act 2003 and sections 5,9(8), 9ZA(1), 9ZA(2) of the Wireless Telegraphy Act 2006</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>45(5)</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p />
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Sections 8B, 9ZA and 2(3) of the Wireless Telegraphy Act 2006</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>45(6)</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p />
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Sections 8B(5) and 9ZA(7) of the Wireless Telegraphy Act 2006</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>45(7)</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p />
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Section 9ZB of the Wireless Telegraphy Act 2006</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Article 46</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Authorisation of the use of radio spectrum</p>
              </td>
