            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>46(1)</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p> </p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Sections 3(1), 3(2), 8, 9 and in particular 8(3B), 8(4) and 8(5), 9(7) of the Wireless Telegraphy Act 2006 and sections 3(2) and 3(3) of the Communications Act 2003. Also section 8(5)(ca) of the Wireless Telegraphy Act 2006 as amended by 80 of Schedule 1 to the draft Regulations. Section 8(3A) is updated by paragraph 80 of Schedule 1 to the draft Regulations</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>46(2)</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p />
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Sections 3(2), 8(3B) and 9(7) of the Wireless Telegraphy Act 2006</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Article 47</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>Conditions attached to individual rights of use for radio spectrum </p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p />
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p>47(1)</p>
              </td>
              <td style="border:1pt solid #000000">
                <p> </p>
